isn't expected to ask for permission
to come in

111
00:16:52,004 --> 00:16:55,735
Papa! How did you get to know...?

112
00:17:02,448 --> 00:17:05,246
It's your happiness I cherish

113
00:17:06,118 --> 00:17:07,449
Be seated, Rajesh

114
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:14,955
Your parents... your family... why
is no one else here from your side?

115
00:17:15,594 --> 00:17:19,394
I'm an orphan, sir.
I'm the only family I have

116
00:17:19,732 --> 00:17:22,758
So what? When Pratima and I
got married, all we had...

117
00:17:22,935 --> 00:17:25,495
were a pair of dresses each.
And by and by...

118
00:17:25,671 --> 00:17:27,866
by dint of my efforts,
I built this empire

119
00:17:28,173 --> 00:17:33,941
