"You're drunk!
- But I think..."

156
00:22:13,859 --> 00:22:22,665
"you're quite helpless.
Who are you...?"

157
00:22:22,934 --> 00:22:26,836
"Who you are, I don't even know"

158
00:22:46,058 --> 00:22:47,992
Hey, I'm still single, I swear

159
00:22:51,263 --> 00:22:55,597
My dark little, darling sister

160
00:23:07,913 --> 00:23:10,677
How's my son?
- I'm fine

161
00:23:14,386 --> 00:23:21,189
Look at her! Time so soon for
my little blossom to get married?

162
00:23:23,695 --> 00:23:28,223
Looking so pretty... and the henna
on your hands too?

163
00:23:28,533 --> 00:23:32,697
May God bestow upon these hands
all the happiness, forever

164
00:23:33,038 --> 00:23:35,404
Where's Papa?

165
